PART 2: Kraken – Crypto-Only (No Stocks)
2.1 Current State
As of 2026, Kraken does not offer stocks, ETFs, or options trading. It remains a cryptocurrency-only exchange.

Kraken briefly offered tokenized stocks in 2021-2022 (through a partnership allowing trading of tokenized Apple, Tesla, etc. on the blockchain), but this service was discontinued due to regulatory pressure. The /0/public/AssetPairs endpoint no longer returns any stock-like instruments.

